|---|---|---|
| **Memory unit** | Encrypted content blob + metadata | Self-describing Memory DNA with embedded decoders, provenance, temporal commitments |
| **Connections** | Parent references in DAG | Typed, weighted Hebbian edges (causal, temporal, semantic, contradictory, hierarchical, analogical) |
| **Organization** | Manual tags + memory types | Self-organizing via Hebbian learning + Dream Engine consolidation + ontological lenses |
| **Retrieval** | Semantic + keyword search | MQL (computable queries) + multi-index planning + anticipatory pre-loading + lensed views |
| **Understanding** | Extraction + basic prediction | Cognitive Twin (knowledge map, reasoning profile, decision model, emotional map) |
| **Background processing** | None | Dream Engine: consolidation, pattern discovery, contradiction detection, decay, anticipation, schema evolution |
| **Temporal model** | Single timestamp + recency decay | Multi-dimensional time (event, creation, learning, access, predicted utility) + half-life decay + temporal projections |
| **Access control** | Per-recipient encryption | Self-enforcing ABE policies + proxy re-encryption + time-locked crypto |
| **Verifiability** | Content signatures | Merkle-chained provenance + temporal commitments + ZK proofs of knowledge |
| **Persistence** | Local storage + cloud backup | Century-scale Memory Capsules with embedded decoders, crypto agility, inheritance |
| **Collaboration** | Circle-based sharing | Collective memory spaces, composable cross-user queries, consent protocol, structure forking |
| **Interoperability** | AI provider integration | Universal Memory Protocol (UMP), Memory API, domain plugins |
| **Self-awareness** | None | Meta-memories, retrieval analytics, confidence scoring, explicit uncertainty |
| **User control** | CRUD + export | + Cognitive Twin inspection/correction, Dream Engine approval, constitutional constraints, memory due process |
| **Scale ceiling** | ~100K memories | Designed for millions of memories over decades; multi-index retrieval in <100ms |
| **Modalities** | Text only | Native multimodal: text, audio, image, video, code, spatial, structured |
| **Compression** | None | Lossy compression with fidelity markers + multi-fidelity latent representations |
| **Query language** | Keyword/semantic search | Full MQL: temporal analysis, pattern detection, counterfactual simulation, cross-user composition |
| **Ethical guardrails** | User controls data | + Constitutional constraints, algorithmic accountability, bias auditing, cognitive liberty protections |

